<item>
            <title>[SOLR-8175] Wordbreak spellchecker throws IOOBE with Occur.MUST term</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-8175</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Using the WordBreakSolrSpellChecker, if a user queries for &quot;+foo barbaz&quot; and &quot;bar baz&quot; is a suggestion for &quot;barbaz&quot;, Solr will throw an IndexOutOfBoundsException.  As a result, a server driven by user queries might throw a certain percentage of HTTP 500 responses as users hit this.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
